
The "Local" part of the layout is everything below the context banner
and above the footer.

It should have one of the following structures:
 
option 0: full width
-------------------------------

#local.full_width
  #column_center
    %article#content

option 1: with sidebar
------------------------------

on the left side:

#local.sidebar.on_left
  #column_left
    %nav#local_nav
  #column_center
    %article#content

on the right side:

#local.sidebar.on_right
  #column_center
    %article#content
  #column_right
    %nav#local_nav

option 3: with side column
------------------------------

side column is wider than the sidebar

a left side column:

#local.sidecolumn.on_left
  #column_left
  #column_center
    %article#content

a right side column:

#local.sidecolumn.on_right
  #column_center
    %article#content
  #column_right


